    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "IIRC tooltips just became upgradable, so you really don't need this. You can upgrade stats through applying a statmultiplier and armaments are upgradable for a great while ago. The With* traits are all upgradable (excluding WithDeathAnimation, which is the sole \"reason\" why the RA2 WithSwimSuit is needed).\r\n\r\nIOW: you should be capable of doing everything to \"upgrade\" a unit  externally to something else. It does require careful planning atm - I acknowledge this is a case where the condition setup will simplify this - and you shouldn't need to upgrade any Render* traits for this."
  },
